## Limitations

This report is based on data and information available up to October 2023. The rapidly changing nature of the automotive market and economic conditions may lead to new developments that are not covered in this report. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, the complexity of global supply chains and economic factors means that some nuances may not be fully captured. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive analysis.